snippet.textDisplay:
The music arrangement of this song should be taught in music schools. The sense of proportion displayed by the music producer and executed by the musicians are prime example of how new age-non traditional-traditional music instruments can be at used to enhance a classic of Bangla music and not to ruin it. 

On a personal note, this Robindra Songit was the morning anthem of my Choto Chachu, lots of fond memories revolve around this song. 

Thank you Coke Studio Bangla from the bottom of my heart
